ivardefs.name: endpoint
ivardefs.desc: The uri that describes the actual end-point to send messages to.

ivardefs.name: header_
ivardefs.desc: Additional headers / information to send as part of the notification.

ivardefs.name: payload
ivardefs.desc: The mime type to send the payload in - either application/fhir+xml, or application/fhir+json. If the payload is not present, then there is no payload in the notification, just a notification.

ivardefs.name: type
ivardefs.desc: The type of channel to send notifications on.

properties.desc: Details where to send notifications when resources are received that meet the criteria.
